item.title: Importance
item.description:
Importance

I was talking with my students today and one of them made the claim that The Force Awakens was going to be the most important movie of all time. I eventually stared him down to "most important movie of our generation." I then told him I didn't think that it was going to be important, which started a discussion on what it meant for a movie to be important and what some important movies were.Â
